所有程序包的分层结构

程序包分层结构:
  • io,
  • method,
  • ui,
  • vo

类分层结构

  • java.lang.Object
    • method.accountCk (implements method.accountCheck)
    • method.Bank
    • method.clearFund (implements method.clear)
    • ui.clearFunds
    • ui.closeAccount
    • vo.currentAccount (implements java.io.Serializable, vo.withdrawalNotice)
      • vo.juniorAccount
      • vo.saverAccount (implements vo.withdrawalNotice)
    • method.depositAmountCheck (implements method.depositAmount)
    • ui.depositFunds
    • method.duplicationCheck
    • io.fileio
    • ui.home
    • method.juniorCheckTest (implements method.juniorCheck)
    • mainRun
    • ui.openAccount
    • ui.suspendFunds
    • vo.test
    • method.withdrawAccountCheck (implements method.withdrawCheck)
    • ui.withdrawFunds
